Package: PenHMM
Type: Package
Title: Penalized Hidden Markov Models with Covariates in the Measurement Model
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Luca", family = "Brusa", email = "luca.brusa@unimib.it", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to simulate, estimate, and cross-validate discrete-time hidden Markov models with covariates in the measurement model using a penalized maximum likelihood approach. The penalty regularizes the dispersion of the state-specific support points to address latent-state separation.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    Formula,
    LMest,
    MASS,
    stats
Suggests:
    future,
    future.apply
